title: Ebro In The Morning - YeeHaws, WooHoos, and Monkeypox
itunes:author: Ebro In The Morning on HOT 97
itunes:summary:
Ebro, Rosenberg and Laura Stylez star in HOT97's flagship program Ebro in the Morning - this episode aired on 7/26/2022.

Ebro, Rosenberg, Laura Stylez and the crew are in the studio discussing the YeeHaw's and Woo Hoo's that white people make, the pronunciation and death of the Choco Taco, and the spread of Monkeypox.

All that and more on Ebro In The Morning!

Subscribe to "Summer Jam: Through The Years" - hosted by Laura Stylez!
